<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">有机废气吸收剂</span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">有机废气处理方法有许多，但是低成本高效易操作等优点的只有吸收法，本产品MJJ_179也解决了传统吸收药剂吸收容量低的问题，将使用时间延长至一月，而且仅需添加少量MJJ_180补充液即可。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">安鸿防滑剂</span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 32px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">1、高效防滑：使用前后的表面摩擦系数大幅度提升，地面越湿滑，效果越显著。颠覆传统防滑概念：目前市场销售的防滑砖，只是利用表层的凹凸不平来防滑，遇水或遇油后失去效力，并不防滑。而经本公司防滑剂处理过后的地面，遇水、遇油可以在其上面跑步绝对不滑，一经防滑处理防滑效果长期有效。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 32px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">2、不改变瓷砖原貌：防滑处理后，不会损伤地面原有风貌，几乎看不出有任何的变化与影响，保持了地砖原有风貌</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white;" />
</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、效果持久：喷涂一次，常规使用频率可以保持5年防滑效果。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white;" />
</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4、环保安全：本品为高分子水性聚合物，对环境无污染，使用后不会产生对人体有害的残留物。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white;" />
</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5、使用方便：小面积，不需专业施工，自已动手做防滑。</span></p>
